      <title>消费者价格不变为美联储考虑降息提供空间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/unchanged-consumer-prices-to-give-fed-room-to-consider-rate-cuts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据彭博经济研究公司称，周二到期的劳工统计局月度报告将显示 11 月份消费者价格再次保持不变，这为美联储在未来几个月考虑降低利率提供了空间。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-12/unchanged-consumer-prices-to-give-fed-room-to-consider-rate-cuts</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 12 Dec 2023 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
